<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5310806>
    dc:description "Figs 6–11. 6–8 – Chrysodema (Gelaeus) florensis Lansberge, 1880 (lectotype ♂, 25.75 mm). 9–11 – C. (G.) foraminifera Lansberge, 1879 (lectotype ♀, 25.25 mm). 6, 9 – dorsal view; 7, 10 – ventral view; 8, 11 – lateral view." ;
